      "Long-form YouTube video editing (10+ minute format)",
      "Creative visual assets specialized for paid ads (Meta & TikTok Ads Banner)",
      "Access to dedicated cloud storage folder",
      "Revision: Free progressively during active production phase"
    ] : [
      "Volume produksi kuantitas video pendek dan visual gambar disesuaikan penuh",
      "Editing video konten YouTube durasi panjang (Format 10+ menit ke atas)",
      "Aset kreatif visual khusus performa kampanye iklan berbayar (Meta & TikTok Ads)",
      "Akses folder penyimpanan komparatif (Cloud storage dedicated server)",
      "Revisi: Bebas bertahap selama alur masa produksi aktif"
    ]
  }
